S.FORM: nu di'tuan a bulad nilacul ayza a bulad u ka sidi'tuan a bulad hansa likaten namu cacay a tinghuy, kya a mapalemed tu mihmihcaan. balaki tu sa, cayay katalaw tu ditu', u sakatalawan uynian u mihecaan. nika mihecaan cayay pisulul tu tademaw. 歳月一定不饒人

no di'toan a bolad nilacol ayza a bolad o ka sidi'toan a bolad hansa likaten namo cacay a tinghoy, kya a mapalemed to mihmihcaan. balaki to sa, cayay katalaw to dito', o sakatalawan oynian o mihecaan. nika mihecaan cayay pisolol to tademaw. 歳月一定不饒人
